Description: Saga Pure ASA, formerly known as Saga Tankers ASA, is a Norway-based investment and management Company related to industry, energy, real estate, including ownership and investment in other businesses. The Company seeks out and invests in companies within renewable energy, hydrogen, circular economy and reduction of CO2 emissions. The Company's portfolio consists of such entities as Bergen Carbon Solutions, Horisont Energi, Heimdall Power, IC Technology, Hyon, Everfuel and Pryme. The Company operates domestically.
